Military Popularity: [+ sorbonne_military_pop +]%

Civilian Popularity: [+ sorbonne_civilian_pop +]%

**Legalists**: Legalists are those who supported Lott's counter-coup. They are the fiercest defenders of the Constitution in the military and will stop at nothing to prevent a coup.

Military Popularity: [+ legalist_military_pop +]%

Civilian Popularity: [+ legalist_civilian_pop +]%

**Praças**: They are the military faction most loyal to João Goulart. Entirely composed of low-ranking officers who seek enfranchisement. Many of them were present during the Campanha da Legalidade.

